## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef578-102"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>才會發生事件時<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>控制<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A>屬性設定或其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A>屬性是`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef578-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event occurs only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A> property is set or its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A> property is `true`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef578-103">當您處理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>事件，您指定的處理常式中的工具提示文字會顯示每當滑鼠指標位在儲存格和控制項<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ShowCellToolTips%2A>屬性值是`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef578-103">When you handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event, the ToolTip text you specify in the handler is shown whenever the mouse pointer is over a cell and the control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ShowCellToolTips%2A> property value is `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef578-104"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>事件很有用，當您想要顯示的目前狀態或儲存格的值所決定的工具提示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef578-104">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event is useful when you want to display ToolTips determined by the current state or value of a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef578-105"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>也就會發生事件時的值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>已擷取屬性，或是以程式設計的方式，或當滑鼠指標進入儲存格。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef578-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event also occurs whenever the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is retrieved, either programmatically or when the mouse pointer enters a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef578-106">您可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A>並<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A>屬性來判斷狀態或儲存格，並使用此資訊來設定<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef578-106">You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A> properties to determine the state or value of a cell, and use this information to set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ef578-107">這個屬性會使用儲存格的值初始化<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A>屬性，它會覆寫的事件值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef578-107">This property is initialized with the value of the cell <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> property, which the event value overrides.</span></span>  
  
